{"tid":469740,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[M記見聞]究竟d死廢老可以有幾唔要面","createTime":"2017-11-15T15:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T04:14:12.000Z","uid":70786,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb8d69f3fca365220a75ace74305b829788e7c1","tid":469740,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n頭先去M記自助點餐<br />\n側邊就係甜品部<br />\n聽到個死廢老拎住杯新地係度屌個十零歲M記仔<br />\n「你都好手勢喇，唧到個筒中間一d雪糕都冇，你特登係個邊唧上去唔唧中間，你學壞師呀！」一路走就一路跳線咁「你學壞師呀！」見住個M記仔好無奈咁戥佢唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為左一杯幾蚊嘅雪糕都要俾說話人聽<br />\nd死廢老幾時中風死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46412213ea3e3a9899c8467da246d00b4996af5","tid":469740,"uid":44814,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:31:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得最恐怖係喺個度過夜個啲乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個次2點落街食 嚇撚死我 難民營咁"},{"pid":"b79c5b50d0339a093cb9eb31348ae4934e87f7c6","tid":469740,"uid":72608,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"係香港做過服務業都知廢老同濕9師奶係最麻煩<br />\n<br />\n郁D就比說話你聽"},{"pid":"1d3f324aee9bd9e4ba72e4f5fec4d2243697e851","tid":469740,"uid":152437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7f2e3095046f8cd3b78c3d451a75bcb97a0a380","tid":469740,"uid":152437,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:44:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"683465c23afe6943609e75347baeee60e00dbf04","tid":469740,"uid":139676,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:57:34.000Z","msg":"阿伯屌得好"},{"pid":"a7f80b6ca6d6f7af8455f64489ce34def2e53e20","tid":469740,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:04:56.000Z","msg":"我岩岩等拎野食, 有個阿叔無啦啦講野好大聲<br />\n&quot;傻仔, 你俾人呃左喇...BLABLABLA&quo